.SH NAME
device_links_driver_cleanup \- Update links after driver removal.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" device_links_driver_cleanup
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
Device whose driver has just gone away.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update links to consumers for \fIdev\fP by changing their status to "dormant" and
invoke \fB__device_links_no_driver\fP to update links to suppliers for it as
appropriate.

Links without the DL_FLAG_MANAGED flag set are ignored.
